kr.buildit.buildthing.ble.service.connection

Class ConnectedBeacon

  • java.lang.Object
    • kr.buildit.buildthing.ble.service.connection.ConnectedBeacon
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ConnectedBeacon
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    커넥션 후 비콘 정보와 값 변경시 사용되는 명령어와 값을 포함한다.
    비콘 값 변경 시 사용되는 메소드
    Manager.changeBeaconValue(kr.buildit.buildthing.ble.service.connection.ConnectedBeacon)
    비콘 값을 변경 할 때 사용되는 명령어 목록
    • Connection.COMMAND_CHANGE_ADVERTISING_INTERVAL
    • Connection.COMMAND_CHANGE_INSTANCE_ID
    • Connection.COMMAND_CHANGE_IO_OUTPUT
    • Connection.COMMAND_CHANGE_MAJOR
    • Connection.COMMAND_CHANGE_MINOR
    • Connection.COMMAND_CHANGE_MODE
    • Connection.COMMAND_CHANGE_NAME
    • Connection.COMMAND_CHANGE_NAMESPACE_ID
    • Connection.COMMAND_CHANGE_PASSWORD
    • Connection.COMMAND_CHANGE_SCHEME_PREFIX
    • Connection.COMMAND_CHANGE_SENSOR_INTERVAL
    • Connection.COMMAND_CHANGE_TX_POWER
    • Connection.COMMAND_CHANGE_URL
    • Connection.COMMAND_CONFIRM_PASSWORD


    일부 명령어는 다음과 같이 미리 정의된 값으로만 변경 가능하다.
    Connection.COMMAND_CHANGE_MODE
    • ConnectionConstants.CONNECTION_MODE_BUILDTHING
    • ConnectionConstants.CONNECTION_MODE_I_BEACON
    • ConnectionConstants.CONNECTION_MODE_EDDYSTONE_UID
    • ConnectionConstants.CONNECTION_MODE_EDDYSTONE_URL
    • ConnectionConstants.CONNECTION_MODE_EDDYSTONE_TLM

    Connection.COMMAND_CHANGE_SCHEME_PREFIX
    • ConnectionConstants.CONNECTION_URL_PREFIX_HTTP_WWW
    • ConnectionConstants.CONNECTION_URL_PREFIX_HTTPS_WWW
    • ConnectionConstants.CONNECTION_URL_PREFIX_HTTP
    • ConnectionConstants.CONNECTION_URL_PREFIX_HTTPS

    Connection.COMMAND_CHANGE_TX_POWER
    • ConnectionConstants.CONNECTION_TX_POWER_M_20
    • ConnectionConstants.CONNECTION_TX_POWER_M_16
    • ConnectionConstants.CONNECTION_TX_POWER_M_12
    • ConnectionConstants.CONNECTION_TX_POWER_M_8
    • ConnectionConstants.CONNECTION_TX_POWER_M_4
    • ConnectionConstants.CONNECTION_TX_POWER_0
    • ConnectionConstants.CONNECTION_TX_POWER_4
